# Ultimate Guide: How to Create a Honeypot Token on Ethereum

Learn **how to create a honeypot token** with this step-by-step **Ethereum smart contract tutorial**. This guide covers building a **honeypot ERC-20 token** using **Solidity programming**, deploying it with **Remix IDE**, and testing on **Sepolia testnet**. Perfect for **blockchain developers** exploring **DeFi token creation**, **smart contract development**, or **cryptocurrency experiments**.
